snippet.textDisplay:
@1:15:50 It occurs to me: the fact that they're bringing THIS level of energy
to an empty room, because they love the fans and they love the music, and
and they went to the trouble of setting up this magnificent private concert,
THIS is exactly why the Dropkick Murphys are the best of the best <3

I'm watching this again cuz it genuinely helped me ease into the Quarantine,
find some lightness and joy and memories of the DKM-SPD concerts that
that I've had the pleasure to attend -- and this is all the best, of how you can
roll into this weird suddenly-new-Era of #QuarantineLife.

God bless all of you on that stage, & the folx involved in setting it all up.
Stay safe, stay well, and (keyne hore) please stay healthy during this plague.
Y'all are shining stars, in this moment of darkness, and this concert is an
an absolutely unforgettable gift on a day of such strange sudden lockdown.

(Proverbs 28:13).

***(Psalms 32:5)<---I acknowledged my sin unto thee, and mine iniquity have I not hid. I said, I will confess my transgressions unto the LORD; and thou forgavest the iniquity of my sin.

***(Psalms 38:18)<---For I will declare mine iniquity; I will be sorry for my sin.

***(2 Corinthians 7:10)<---For godly sorrow produces repentance leading to salvation not to be regretted: but the sorrow of the world produces death.
